ombaga kuza mu rukiko yaba abacamanza n’abashinjacyaha, hari naho bagiye bafata icyemezo cyo guhagarika amaburanisha burundu.
Urugero rwa hafi twafata Urubanza rwa Kabuga Felesiyani rwashyikirijwe Urwego rwashyiriweho gusoza imirimo yasizwe n’urukiko mpuzamahanga mpanabyaha rwashyiriweho u Rwanda (IRMCT), rwagombaga kuburanishirizwa Arusha muri Tanzaniya ariko kubera ingamba zo gukumira ikwirakwira rya koronavirusi, Umuyobozi wa IRMCT ategeka ko Kabuga yoherezwa mu Buholandi arinaho Kabuga yagar
... (506 chars skipped) ...
 jenoside, naho hagiye habaho ubwo bukererwe, inkiko zafunze imiryango kubera koronavirusi imanza zabo ntizihuta.
Amazina y’abakurikiranyweho icyaha cya jenoside bagombaga kuba baburana muri ibi bihe twugarijwe na COVID19.
